An official letter from Caijing magazine.
《财经》杂志由中国证券市场研究中心主办，1998年创刊，秉承“独立、独家、独到”的新闻理念，以权威性、公正性、专业性报道见长，是政经学界决策者、研究者、管理者的必读刊物。
"Caijing" magazine, sponsored by the China Securities Market Research Center, was founded in 1998, upholding the news concept of "independence, exclusivity and originality," and providing authoritative, impartial and professional reports.
。
.
文|《财经》数据研究员 徐进图|《财经》视觉中心编辑 | 谢丽容1. 今日概况：根据国家卫健委数据，2月11日0—24时，31个省（自治区、直辖市）和新疆生产建设兵团报告，新增确诊病例2015例（湖北1638例），重症病例增加871例（湖北897例），新增死亡病例97例（湖北94例，河南、湖南、重庆各1例），新增疑似病例3342例（湖北1685例）。
At 0 to 2400 hours on February 11, 31 provinces (autonomous regions and municipalities directly under the Central Government) and the Xinjiang Production and Construction Corps reported new cases of confirmed cases (1,638 in Hubei), 871 new cases (897 each in Hubei, Hunan and Chongqing), and 3,342 new suspected cases (1 each in Hubei, Hunan and Chongqing).
图12. 新增病例：武汉战局扭转，其他地区继续向好图2国内非湖北地区微降，降速减缓。
Figure 12. New cases: Wuhan war situation reversed, other regions continue to good figure 2 domestic non-Hubei region slightly declined, deceleration.
图3湖北非武汉地区继续下降，下降趋势得以巩固。
Fig. 3 Hubei non-Wuhan area continues to decline, the downward trend has been consolidated.
数字显示，紧邻武汉的孝感、黄冈以及随州、荆州、襄阳等1000例病例以上城市新增病例均出现过跳升、陡升而后稳定、回落。
Figures show that the next Wuhan filial piety, Huanggang, as well as Suizhou, Jingzhou, Xiangyang more than 1000 cases of urban new cases have appeared jump, steep rise and then stable, fall.
可以推测这些城市的洪峰大约已分别在2日1日-5日期间通过。
It can be surmised that the flood peaks of these cities have been adopted in the period between February 1 and 5 respectively.
图4图5武汉新增病例数出现确认性回落。
Fig. 4 FIG. 5 The number of new cases in Wuhan shows a positive decrease.
2月6号以来，武汉在中央指导组直接指挥督导下发起攻坚战，对确诊、疑似、未明发热和密切接触者“四类人员“进行全市彻底排查，做到”应收尽收、不漏一人“。
Since February 6, Wuhan, under the direct command and supervision of the Central Steering Group, has launched an offensive and determined war to carry out a thorough citywide survey of the four categories of persons identified, suspected, unsure of fever and in close contact, so as to make sure that no one is missing or lost.
综合数据和一线报道，显示此战大局已定，形势正发生根本性扭转。
Comprehensive data and first-line reports indicate that the war is over and that the situation is fundamentally turning around.
3. 确诊病例增长率：武汉增速回落至6%以下，湖北非武汉地区降至4%图6武汉增长率回落到6%以下，倍增时间延长到12天以上。
The growth rate of confirmed cases in Wuhan has dropped to less than 6 percent, that in Hubei province has dropped to 4 percent, and that of Wuhan has dropped to below 6 percent, and the doubling time has been extended to more than 12 days.
湖北非武汉地区下降到4%，倍增时间延长到18天以上。
Hubei non-Wuhan area fell to 4%, the doubling time was extended to more than 18 days.
4.尚在接受医学观察人数下降图7非湖北地区接受医学观察人数连续5日下降。
Figure 7 The number of people receiving medical observation in non-Hubei area declined for 5 consecutive days.
5.待排查疑似病例今天是湖北开始发布此待排查数据的第四天。
5. Suspected cases are due to be cleared today is the fourth day Hubei started to release the pending data.
湖北每日新增疑似病例反弹后已连续两日下降。
The daily increase in suspected cases in Hubei province has declined for two consecutive days.
图8我们看出国内非湖北地区稳步趋降。
Fig. 8 shows that the non-Hubei area in China is declining steadily.
湖北在连续两日下降基础上，继续大幅下降5000多例。
On the basis of two consecutive days of decline, Hubei continued to drop by more than 5,000 cases.
但值得注意的是，湖北从今天起发布了“新增临床诊断病例”4890例和“现有临床诊断病例”10567例以及“疑似病例、临床诊断病例集中隔离”15514人。
However, it is worth noting that from today, Hubei released 4,890 new cases of clinical diagnosis and 10,567 cases of existing clinical diagnosis, as well as 15,514 cases of suspected cases and concentrated isolation of clinical diagnosis cases.
此项新分类可能会分流部分疑似病例，应与武汉攻坚战“应收尽收”有关。
The new classification may divert some suspected cases and should be related to the "receivable" of the Wuhan Jianquan War.
此处可比口径也许用15514人更为合理。
A comparable calibre of 15,514 would make more sense here.
国内非湖北地区稳步下降。
The non-Hubei area declined steadily.
6.在院治疗人数图9非湖北区呈现稳定。
6. The number of people treated in hospital was stable in non-Hubei region.
湖北地区住院治疗人数继续增加，增幅减小。
The number of hospitalized patients in Hubei continued to increase and decrease.
7. 新增治愈和病死率图10国内非湖北地区、武汉新治愈人数都在增加，湖北非武汉有所回落。
Figure 10 The number of newly cured cases in non-Hubei areas and Wuhan is on the increase, and Hubei non-Wuhan has decreased.
图11非湖北地区新增治愈与新增确诊的交叉点近在咫尺。
Fig. 11 Non-Hubei area new treatment and newly diagnosed intersection near at hand.
“拐点”将至！图12由于病程发展，经过一段时间后，病死率在此阶段持续小幅回升当属正常。
Fig. 12 Due to the progression of the disease, it is normal for the fatality rate to continue to rise slightly over time.
因为疫情暴发初期，每日入院新增病例猛增，经过一段时间滞后，会带来死亡人数的较快增加；另一方面，随着疫情得到控制，每日新增确诊病例会出现明显下降。
Because of the surge in the number of new admissions per day in the early stages of the outbreak, there will be a relatively rapid increase in the number of deaths after a time lag; on the other hand, there will be a significant decrease in the number of newly confirmed cases per day as the outbreak is brought under control.
这一增（分子）一降（分母），一定会导致病死率回升。
This increase (numerator) a drop (denominator), will certainly lead to an increase in the fatality rate.
只有在疫情基本结束这个数值才会真正逼近“最终病死率”。
Only at the end of the epidemic will this figure really approximate the "final fatality rate."
小结：武汉攻坚成功，全局扭转。
Summary: Wuhan Jianxian success, global reversal.
非湖北地区“拐点”将至。
Non-Hubei "inflection point" is approaching.
